  "prompt": "I'm new to Quora. What does it mean when someone says they are following me?",
  "response": "Welcome to Quora! When someone says they are following you on the platform, it means they are interested in your contributions and want to see your activity. Following you allows them to receive updates about your new posts, answers, and any other content you interact with. It\u2019s a way for users to keep track of people whose insights or knowledge they find valuable. Similarly, you can also follow other users whose content you enjoy or want to learn from.",
